00:26:35,120 --> 00:26:38,440
You worked at courthouses for years. You must still have some connections.
你在法院工作了多年  你一定还保持联系

334
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:43,520
People with priors. Ex-prisoners. I thought maybe...
有前科的人  进过监狱的人 我想可能……

335
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:46,080
Maybe what, Taci?
也许什么，塔奇 ？

336
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:48,720
Could you find me a killer, Agah?
也许你能为我找出杀手，阿加

337
00:26:51,360 --> 00:26:52,560
Excuse me?
什么？

338
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:55,000
A killer.
杀手

339
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:56,760
A killer.
杀手

340
00:26:57,440 --> 00:26:58,760
For you.
为你

341
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:05,200
What do you mean, they gathered up the women? What does she want?
什么意思，聚集了这些女人？她想要什么？

342
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:09,360
She's supposedly going to find the girl that Tayyar raped.
据说她要找到塔亚尔强奸的那个女孩

343
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:13,240
Oh God!
天啊！

344
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:16,760
Alright, you hold tight. I'll think of something.
好吧，你稳住  我想想办法

345
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:20,440
Are they gone now? Nevra and the others?
他们现在走了吗？内芙拉他们？

346
00:27:20,520 --> 00:27:23,520
They're gone. They stopped by the burnt-down house.
他们走了  又去被烧毁的房子了

347
00:27:23,600 --> 00:27:25,480
Took some more photos.
拍了一些照片

348
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:27,400
What are they looking for at that house?
他们在那房子找什么？

349
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:30,280
Vural...
乌拉尔……

350
00:27:32,320 --> 00:27:33,560
Tear it down.
拆了它

351
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:38,280
Get a bulldozer today. Tear the house down.
今天就买一辆推土机  把房子推了

352
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:40,080
Bury the rubble.
碎砖瓦都埋起来

353
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:43,000
I don't want them getting anything out of that house.
我不想让他们从那所房子里得到任何东西

354
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:46,200
Level the place. You got that?
把那房子夷为平地  明白了吗？

355
00:27:46,760 --> 00:27:47,960
Of course.
明白

356
00:27:56,280 --> 00:27:57,600
Forgive me, Zuhal.
原谅我，祖哈尔

357
00:27:58,800 --> 00:28:01,280
They come to me with the most ridiculous questions.
他们找我问一个愚蠢的问题

358
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:09,320
You know how I feel sometimes?
你知道有时候我是什么感觉吗？

359
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:13,240
As though they loaded the whole world on my back,
仿佛他们把整个世界都压在我的背上，

360
00:28:13,320 --> 00:28:15,160
and they keep telling me to get a move on.
并且不断让我继续前进

361
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:18,960
Throw off your burden, then. Throw it off and be free.
那么，甩掉你的负担吧  扔掉它，重获自由

362
00:28:20,040 --> 00:28:23,120
How am I supposed to do that? I live in that world also.
我应该怎么做？我还生活在那个世界里

363
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:28,920
Fine. Leave some of it for me, then. Let me carry some of it.
好吧  负担也给我一些，我们一起背

364
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:33,440
You're already carrying me. That's more than enough.
你已经在背负我了  那已经足够了

365
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,920
I get it now.
我明白了

366
00:28:39,120 --> 00:28:40,120
You get what?
明白什么了？

367
00:28:40,800 --> 00:28:43,200
Why my dad loves you so much.
为什么我爸爸这么爱你

368
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:52,200
So?
怎么？

369
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:55,280
You're going to die, huh?
你快死了吧？

370
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:00,960
I'm going to die, alright...
是的  我快死了……

371
00:29:01,840 --> 00:29:04,120
But it's proving to be very painful.
但事实证明，这是非常痛苦的

372
00:29:04,760 --> 00:29:06,440
It's a prick of an illness.
这是一种疾病

373
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:11,320
It's seen predominantly in Turkish people.
主要出现在土耳其人身上

374
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:13,200
I wonder why.
我想知道为什么

375
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:17,360
There are these pockets of air in the lungs.
肺里有这些空气囊

376
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:22,120
Little stones form inside them. Like grains of sand.
里面会形成沙粒一样的结石

377
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:24,120
What's it called?
什么病？

378
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:26,600
Alveolar Microlithiasis.
肺泡微结石症

379
00:29:27,760 --> 00:29:28,840
I see.
知道了

380
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:32,600
It's seen in Turkish people, but the name's not in Turkish.
是在土耳其人身上发现的  但是却不是以土耳其语命名

381
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,600
Yes. Well...
是的

382
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:38,360
That's why, Agah... I want to die.
这就是为什么，阿加，我想死

383
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,000
I can't take it anymore.
我受不了了

384
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:43,400
I have my wits about me still.
我还算有点理智

385
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:47,360
My arms and legs still work. I want to go while I still have all that.
我的胳膊和腿也还能用  我想在我仍然能自理的时候离开

386
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:48,880
I can't kill myself.
我不能自杀

387
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:51,040
I tried. I tried time and again.
我试过一次又一次

388
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:55,320
But life grabs you so tightly that it's impossible to get free.
但是生活紧紧地抓住了你，以至于无法获得自由

389
00:29:57,800 --> 00:30:00,480
Life... Wraps itself around your neck.
生活环绕在你的脖子上

390
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:06,960
I'd like someone to come...
我希望有人……

391
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:10,880
Put a bullet in my spine, and set me free.
把子弹打在我的脊椎上，让我自由

392
00:30:12,080 --> 00:30:13,160
You're right...
你是对的……

393
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:16,520
I always loved this side of yours.
我一直喜欢你这点

394
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:22,200
You used to say that if you studied law, you would want to become
你曾经说过，如果你学习法律

395
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:27,840
neither prosecutor, nor judge, nor lawyer.
你既不想做检察官，也不想做法官或律师

396
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:29,880
- I'd like to become a notary. - Yes!
-我想当公证人-是的！

397
00:30:30,680 --> 00:30:33,000
Being a notary is perfect for you.
做公证人对你来说简直完美

398
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:38,120
This is what being a notary is like. A notary doesn't ask questions.
公证人就是这样  公证人不问问题

399
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,680
He doesn't judge you...
他不审判你

400
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:46,680
He bears witness, puts down his seal, then turns around and leaves.
公证，盖章，然后转身离开

401
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:49,760
So, Agah?
所以  阿加？

402
00:30:50,840 --> 00:30:54,080
Is there someone who'd kill me? Could you find me someone?
有没有人愿意杀我的？你能找到这个人吗？

403
00:33:37,280 --> 00:33:38,560
How are you doing?
你好吗？

404
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:40,800
You can imagine.
你可以想象

405
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,720
Any news?
有什么消息吗？

406
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:46,720
- No. - What do you mean, no?
-没有  -你是什么意思，没有？

407
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:48,200
Not one fucking change.
没有一点改变

408
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:50,720
They made a mistake with the list.
他们把清单弄错了

409
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:54,840
The heart was compatible with someone else.
心脏不匹配

410
00:33:57,800 --> 00:33:59,960
Alright. Fine.
好吧

411
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:03,440
How's the little Sefa doing?
小塞法过得好吗？

412
00:34:04,360 --> 00:34:06,760
As you can see. He's tired. Sleeping.
如你所见  他睡着了

413
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:09,640
I didn't want to wake him up.
我不想叫醒他

414
00:34:10,560 --> 00:34:11,680
Good. Good.
好

415
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:16,320
- It was so funny the other day. - What was?
-前几天真有趣  -怎么了？

416
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:19,000
The boys at the station were having a ball.
局里的男孩们正在打球

417
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:21,720
Come on, not you!
不是吧！

418
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:25,440
What do you mean, "around 5.11 in height"?
你是什么意思，“身高1米56”？

419
00:34:25,520 --> 00:34:28,400
Not 6 feet. 5.11.
不是1米83  而是1米56

420
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:31,600
I could tell from your voice.
我能从你的声音中听出来

421
00:34:31,680 --> 00:34:34,080
You were in a panic for letting him get a way.
你因他得逞而惊慌失措

422
00:34:34,160 --> 00:34:37,760
How could I not be? It happened again after all these years.
怎么会不惊慌  这么多年之后情景重现

423
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:42,120
It says 5.11 in his report.
他的报告中说1米56

424
00:34:42,200 --> 00:34:46,240
Not around 5.11, 5.11 exactly.
不是大约1米56  而是正好1米56

425
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:49,160
But I was more concerned about your situation.
但我更担心你的情况

426
00:34:49,960 --> 00:34:54,800
"I let him get away again," I thought. "There has to be someone helping him."
“我让他又逃走了，”我想  “肯定有人在帮他  ”

427
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:59,080
Another gunfight will break out. Shots will be fired yet again.
另一场枪战即将爆发  枪声会再次响起

428
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:01,320
I was terrified.
我吓坏了

429
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:04,880
- I sometimes wish you'd left me there. - Stop talking nonsense.
-有时候我希望你把我留在那里-别胡说八道

430
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:07,520
I'm serious.
我是认真的

431
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:10,280
I wish you'd leave me there so I could fucking die.
我希望你能把我留在那里，这样我就可以死掉了

432
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:14,360
You jumped into the fray.
你跳入了困境

433
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:18,240
I was out of bullets. They were about to put one in my head.
我没子弹了  他们就要开枪打我的时候

434
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:21,200
You arrived just like Superman.
你就像超人一样到达

435
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:25,360
You should have asked.
你应该问

436
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:28,320
"Do you want to live?"
“你想活着吗？”

437
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:31,400
"Should I save your life?"
“我应该救你的命吗？”

438
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:36,600
- Like my life's worth anything. - Of course it is.
-就像我的生命有意义一样-当然有意义

439
00:35:37,160 --> 00:35:39,480
You got married.
你结婚了

440
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:43,320
Had a beautiful boy. He's in there as we speak.
有了一个漂亮的孩子  我们说话的时候就在那里

441
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:47,160
Gave him Sefa as a name. My boy.
给他起名叫做塞法

442
00:35:49,120 --> 00:35:51,800
Then your wife couldn't stand you and ran away.
然后你的妻子受不了你逃跑了

443
00:35:52,560 --> 00:35:55,040
And you started hating all women.
然后你开始讨厌所有女人

444
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:59,680
Your life was fucked. What else could you ask for?
你的生活很糟，你还能要求什么？

445
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:07,360
- As though yours wasn't. - We're talking about you for now.
-好像你的不糟  -我们现在说的是你

446
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:12,800
Don't you have a home or something? Go home.
你没有家吗？回家吧

447
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:14,040
I do.
我有

448
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:17,400
I do have a home, but there's no one in it.
我有家，但家里没有人

449
00:36:18,640 --> 00:36:20,200
You took that one girl home.
你带那个女孩回了家

450
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:22,800
We did it on the floor. It doesn't count.
我们是在地板上做的  那不算

451
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:37,040
Esin?
内斯林？

452
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,360
What is it, Vural?
什么事，乌拉尔？

453
00:36:41,440 --> 00:36:44,360
- Blown tyre again? - No, it's not that.
-轮胎又爆了吗-不是

454
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:46,480
I was told you were given something for safekeeping.
有人告诉我你有东西要妥善保管

455
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,760
Safekeeping?
保管？

456
00:36:48,800 --> 00:36:50,880
You know how they're tearing the house down?
你知道他们把房子拆掉了吗？

457
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:53,200
You took something from the house. What did you take?
你从屋子里拿走了东西 你拿了什么？

458
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:56,760
Have you completely lost it? Is that why you came all the way here?
你有病吗？这就是为什么你一路跟到这里吗？

459
00:36:56,840 --> 00:36:59,160
Nothing will come out of that house.
房子里的任何东西都不能带出来

460
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:02,160
It's all headed underground.
都要埋到地下

461
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:03,880
Who says?
谁说的？

462
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,000
Cemil?
塞米尔？

463
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:09,440
Tell hi to Cemil for me.
给塞米尔问好

464
00:37:09,520 --> 00:37:13,040
Give back what you took and we'll throw it out for you.
把你拿走的东西交出来，我们会为你扔掉

465
00:37:14,200 --> 00:37:17,360
Sadi? What are you doing, son?
萨迪，你在做什么，孩子？

466
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:19,920
I'll tell your mom! Give it back!
我要告诉你妈妈！还给我！

467
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:24,160
- Come on, don't make this any harder. - Vural, stop snooping!
-拜托，别再为难了  -乌拉尔  快停下！

468
00:37:25,640 --> 00:37:28,680
- Stop going through my stuff! - Give back whatever it is you took.
-别再看我的东西了！-把你拿走的东西交出来

469
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:32,200
You're making a big mistake. Get out of my car!
你犯了个大错误  下车！

470
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:39,240
Auntie, what are you doing? Auntie! Auntie!
阿姨，你在做什么？阿姨！

471
00:37:39,320 --> 00:37:40,560
Auntie, what are you doing?
阿姨  你在做什么？

472
00:37:40,640 --> 00:37:42,640
I told you, you were making a big mistake.
我告诉你，你犯了个大错误

473
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:44,800
You're going to break my neck!
你会扭断我的脖子的！

474
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:47,600
You'll be just fine. What did I tell you?
你会没事的  我刚刚不是告诉你了吗？

475
00:37:48,160 --> 00:37:50,480
- I told you to get lost! - Take it down. I'm begging you!
-我叫你滚蛋！-求求你了，我求求你！

476
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:53,040
Do you think we're children? Do you think this is all a game?
你认为我们是孩子吗？你认为这都是游戏吗？

477
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:55,560
- I'm asking you nicely. - You can stop asking.
-我现在很客气的请求你  -你不用求了

478
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:58,680
Let's start moving.
我们走吧

479
00:38:01,200 --> 00:38:05,520
- Auntie! Let me go! - You're strangling me!
-阿姨，放开我-你要勒死我了！

480
00:38:09,360 --> 00:38:13,000
- Auntie, let me go! - Auntie, let us go! I'm begging you!
-阿姨，让我走！-阿姨，让我们走！求你了！

481
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,680
Bastards!
混蛋！

482
00:38:18,760 --> 00:38:20,640
Now get the fuck out of my face.
现在都他妈给我滚

483
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:27,120
You'll pay for that, Nesrin. You'll pay for that!
你将为此付出代价，内斯林  你将为此付出代价！

484
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:28,720
Move, you idiot!
走  白痴！

485
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:40,840
That's what you get, little shits!
这就是你们的报应，小混蛋！

486
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:53,280
I must've dozed off, Nesrin.
我一定是打瞌睡了，内斯琳

487
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:59,400
They're tearing down the house you threw a stone at.
他们把山上的房子拆了

488
00:39:00,560 --> 00:39:01,920
They're leveling it.
夷为平地

489
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:05,240
It'll all be gone by tomorrow.
明天一切都会消失

490
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:11,760
But...
但……

491
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:14,840
Everyone will forget about it anyway.
每个人都会忘记它

492
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:21,000
I wanted you to know.
我想让你知道

493
00:39:23,200 --> 00:39:24,800
If, after all these years,
这些年来，如果

494
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:28,360
your conscience is plaguing you for throwing that stone...
你的良心因你扔石头困扰着你……

495
00:39:30,680 --> 00:39:32,160
I went there...
我去了那儿……

496
00:39:35,520 --> 00:39:40,840
And I brought you that stone so that your pain isn't for naught.
我给你带来了那块石头，所以你的痛苦不是毫无意义的

497
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:49,960
Sleep well.
好好睡

498
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:21,360
- Cheers. - Cheers.
-干杯-干杯

499
00:40:22,160 --> 00:40:25,680
- What brings you here? - I just felt like it.
-什么风把你刮来了？-我只是喜欢这里

500
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,240
Welcome, then.
那就欢迎你

501
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:30,680
Welcome, but what's wrong with you?
欢迎，但是你怎么了？

502
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:34,760
What's right with me, Timur?
帖木儿，我怎么了？

503
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:39,960
A psycho killer is out on the loose...
一个变态杀手在逃

504
00:40:40,640 --> 00:40:44,160
And here I am enjoying myself, having raki with you.
而我在这里和葡萄酒

