00:53:08,520 --> 00:53:10,880
After that day, he never spoke to me again.
那天过后，他再也没有跟我说话

677
00:53:13,640 --> 00:53:14,920
I see.
我懂了

678
00:53:16,800 --> 00:53:18,320
Halis...
哈里斯……

679
00:53:18,400 --> 00:53:20,240
Did you know Halis?
你认识哈里斯吗？

680
00:53:20,800 --> 00:53:22,000
Halis?
哈里斯？

681
00:53:22,760 --> 00:53:24,280
Fireman.
消防员

682
00:53:24,920 --> 00:53:28,000
Oh, Halis. Yes, I knew him. He passed.
哦，哈里斯，我知道他，他去世了

683
00:53:28,080 --> 00:53:33,360
He put it in his report that a cigarette butt started the fire.
他在报告中说是烟头引起了火灾

684
00:53:34,280 --> 00:53:36,640
Why would he do that? Why would he protect Ufuk?
他为什么要这样做？为什么要保护乌福克？

685
00:53:36,720 --> 00:53:39,640
Why would he hide the fact that Ufuk started the fire?
他为什么会掩盖乌福克纵火的事实？

686
00:53:40,960 --> 00:53:42,680
There was this judge.
有这么一个法官

687
00:53:43,640 --> 00:53:45,520
- Mehmet something? - Mehmet Yurtgil.
-穆罕默德 什么的？-穆罕默德·尤尔吉尔

688
00:53:46,160 --> 00:53:49,000
- I don't know his surname. - Mehmet Yurtgil.
-我不知道他的姓氏-穆罕默德·尤尔吉尔

689
00:53:49,560 --> 00:53:52,640
He came and found me. Told me...
他来找我  告诉我……

690
00:53:53,480 --> 00:53:55,200
I wasn't to tell anyone anything.
我没有告诉过任何人

691
00:53:55,280 --> 00:53:57,240
He told me that the family that died was Romani.
他告诉我，死去的一家人是吉普赛人

692
00:53:57,320 --> 00:54:00,960
If it was heard that a Romani family was burned alive in Kambura,
如果别人听说有一家吉普赛人在坎布拉被活活烧死，

693
00:54:01,040 --> 00:54:04,040
no one would care that they were targeted because of me.
没有人会担心他们是因我而死的

694
00:54:04,120 --> 00:54:07,680
Everyone would assume that they were targeted because of their ethnicity.
所有人都会认为他们的死因是种族

695
00:54:08,640 --> 00:54:09,760
That's what he said.
那就是他跟我说的

696
00:54:09,840 --> 00:54:14,520
Some people had forcibly kicked a Romani family out of Kambura.
有人强行将吉普赛一家人赶出坎布拉

697
00:54:15,760 --> 00:54:17,920
He didn't want Kambura to get a bad rap,
他不想让坎布拉名声扫地

698
00:54:18,000 --> 00:54:22,040
so he told me not to say anything. So I said yes.
他告诉我什么都不要说  所以我答应了他

699
00:54:22,720 --> 00:54:28,320
The judge must've spoken to Halis. That's why he said it was a cigarette.
法官一定对哈里斯说过什么，这就是为什么他说是烟头引发的火灾

700
00:54:28,400 --> 00:54:31,640
What else could he have done? Kambura would've gotten a bad rap.
他还能做什么？会有损坎布拉的名誉

701
00:54:34,880 --> 00:54:35,920
Alright.
好的

702
00:54:36,960 --> 00:54:40,800
You rest for now. We can talk again in the morning. OK?
你先休息吧，我们明天早上再谈  可以吗？

703
00:54:42,320 --> 00:54:45,240
Sure. But I've told you everything.
当然可以，但我已经告诉过你一切

704
00:54:45,840 --> 00:54:48,080
What else is there to talk about?
还有什么要谈的？

705
00:54:48,160 --> 00:54:50,480
I don't know anything else.
其他的我什么都不知道

706
00:55:26,880 --> 00:55:28,080
Good morning.
早上好

707
00:55:36,840 --> 00:55:38,440
How are you feeling? Did you sleep well?
感觉怎么样？睡得好吗？

708
00:55:38,520 --> 00:55:40,680
Yes. I slept alright.
是的，我睡得很好

709
00:55:40,760 --> 00:55:41,760
Thanks.
谢谢

710
00:55:43,880 --> 00:55:46,640
Nevra, can you drop me off at the station today?
内芙拉，你今天可以载我去车站吗？

711
00:55:47,800 --> 00:55:50,080
Of course. Are you going back to Kambura?
当然可以  你要回坎布拉吗？

712
00:55:50,160 --> 00:55:51,440
No.
不是

713
00:55:51,520 --> 00:55:53,040
I'm not going back there again.
我不会再回去了

714
00:55:53,600 --> 00:55:56,400
I'm going to go to Bursa. I have relatives there.
我要去布尔萨  那里有亲戚

715
00:55:59,600 --> 00:56:00,760
I see.
明白

716
00:56:02,360 --> 00:56:03,840
Yeliz, I need to ask you something.
叶莉兹  我要问你一件事

717
00:56:05,320 --> 00:56:07,760
The things you told me last night...
你昨晚告诉我的事情……

718
00:56:07,840 --> 00:56:10,880
There's nothing I can do about them as a cop.
作为警察我无能为力

719
00:56:10,960 --> 00:56:13,200
All the people you mentioned are already dead.
你提到的所有人都已经死了

720
00:56:14,520 --> 00:56:16,200
I don't get it.
我不明白

721
00:56:17,720 --> 00:56:21,840
Why did you run from home? Did you come here just to tell me this?
你为什么要从家里跑出来？你来这里只是为了告诉我吗？

722
00:56:22,800 --> 00:56:24,200
You know why?
你知道为什么吗？

723
00:56:25,200 --> 00:56:28,040
I needed to get it off my chest so much.
我需要把这些话说出来

724
00:56:28,120 --> 00:56:31,640
I've kept quiet for years and years.
我多年来一直保持沉默

725
00:56:31,720 --> 00:56:33,960
And after I got married? Forget about it.
结婚之后

726
00:56:34,760 --> 00:56:36,800
My husband figured it out.
我丈夫发现了

727
00:56:36,880 --> 00:56:40,080
When it was time to have sex, he checked and saw that I was a woman.
到了做爱的时候，他检查了一下，发现我不是处女

728
00:56:43,920 --> 00:56:45,040
Well...
好吧……

729
00:56:45,120 --> 00:56:48,000
I thought he'd kick me out then.
我以为他会把我赶出去

730
00:56:48,600 --> 00:56:51,120
I thought he'd leave me. But he really loved me.
我以为他会离开我  但他是真的爱我

731
00:56:53,640 --> 00:56:56,840
He loved me so much. He told me not to explain.
他太爱我了  他告诉我不用解释

732
00:56:56,920 --> 00:57:01,360
"No matter what you did, don't tell me, I don't want to know about it," he said.
他说：“不管你做过什么，都不要告诉我，我也不想知道  ”

733
00:57:02,640 --> 00:57:03,640
So I kept quiet.
所以我保持沉默

734
00:57:04,360 --> 00:57:08,640
Then, when we couldn't have children, it was his turn to keep quiet.
然后，当我们发现不能有孩子时，轮到他保持沉默了

735
00:57:09,840 --> 00:57:13,600
We kept quiet. Husband and wife. Our whole lives.
我们保持沉默的夫妻生活

736
00:57:17,200 --> 00:57:20,880
Keeping a secret makes you feel like you're in prison.
保守秘密会让你觉得自己像是在监狱里

737
00:57:21,440 --> 00:57:25,880
I wanted to get it off my chest. I wanted to get it out of me.
我想把这些话说出来  甩开它

738
00:57:25,960 --> 00:57:28,320
I wanted to finally breathe and be free.
我想自由的呼吸

739
00:57:28,400 --> 00:57:31,360
I hoped it might do some good.
我希望这样可能会有所帮助

740
00:57:32,080 --> 00:57:33,160
But...
但……

741
00:57:33,680 --> 00:57:36,120
You say there's nothing you can do.
你说你无能为力

742
00:57:37,280 --> 00:57:40,040
I'm sorry. I took so much of your time.
对不起，我占用了你很长时间

743
00:57:40,120 --> 00:57:44,040
I've kept you off more urgent business. I'm really sorry. Please forgive me.
我让你错过了更紧急的事情  我真的很抱歉，请原谅

744
00:57:44,120 --> 00:57:46,040
Don't be silly. That's not what I meant.
别傻了  我不是那个意思

745
00:57:46,120 --> 00:57:48,800
I'm glad that you came. I'm glad that you told me all that.
我很高兴你来了  我很高兴你你把这些事情告诉我

746
00:57:49,840 --> 00:57:50,880
Thanks.
谢谢

747
00:57:50,960 --> 00:57:52,760
Thank you for listening to me.
谢谢你听我说

748
00:57:54,600 --> 00:57:56,200
- Have something to eat. - Alright.
-吃点东西-好的

749
00:58:01,920 --> 00:58:04,040
Well, how was our day?
好了，我们今天过得怎么样？

750
00:58:06,080 --> 00:58:10,520
Good. So you liked the tour.
好，所以你喜欢这次旅行

751
00:58:11,000 --> 00:58:15,440
Great. We'll do it again. We certainly will. Don't worry.
太好了  我们再做一次  当然会的  别担心

752
00:58:15,520 --> 00:58:17,520
Feza. Feza.
费扎

753
00:58:18,320 --> 00:58:20,080
Feza. Feza?
费扎？

754
00:58:21,520 --> 00:58:24,000
We'll do it again...
我们会再做一次

755
00:58:24,080 --> 00:58:25,560
We'll arrange good tours.
我们会安排好旅行

756
00:58:25,640 --> 00:58:27,560
Everything was perfect...
一切都很完美

757
00:58:27,640 --> 00:58:30,280
I'm so glad to hear that.
我很高兴听到这个消息

758
00:58:32,520 --> 00:58:34,960
Feza. Feza.
费扎

759
00:58:39,400 --> 00:58:40,720
This way...
这边……

760
00:58:47,600 --> 00:58:49,920
Call if you need anything, alright?
如有需要，打个电话好吗？

761
00:58:50,000 --> 00:58:52,080
Sure. Of course. Thank you so much.
当然可以，非常感谢

762
00:58:52,160 --> 00:58:53,880
You don't have to wait for the bus to leave.
你不必等着车开走

763
00:58:56,600 --> 00:58:59,200
- Have a good journey. - Thank you. Thank you so much.
-旅途愉快  -谢谢  非常感谢你

764
00:59:23,800 --> 00:59:25,720
- Don't. - You aren't checking it?
-不用  -你不坐车了吗？

765
00:59:25,800 --> 00:59:27,120
No.
不

766
00:59:27,200 --> 00:59:30,960
I hate buses. You should skip it, as well.
我讨厌公共汽车  你也别坐了

767
00:59:50,080 --> 00:59:53,360
So, Feza... How about another journey?
那么，费扎  我们去另一个旅行怎么样？

768
00:59:54,680 --> 00:59:55,880
How about another poem?
另外一首诗？

769
01:00:41,760 --> 01:00:42,800
Hello
喂？

770
01:00:45,040 --> 01:00:46,040
Yes.
是

771
01:00:49,280 --> 01:00:50,680
Yes.
是的

772
01:01:03,280 --> 01:01:06,040
Feza. Come on. We're here.
来吧  费扎  我们到了

773
01:01:06,680 --> 01:01:07,840
Come on.
来吧

774
01:01:10,280 --> 01:01:13,000
It's right there. Just a short walk away. Go on.
就在那儿  几步之遥  加油

775
01:01:15,880 --> 01:01:19,120
This way, Feza. This way.
这边  费扎

776
01:01:19,200 --> 01:01:20,760
Feza? This way.
费扎？这边

777
01:01:34,240 --> 01:01:35,760
This way, Feza.
这边

778
01:01:43,280 --> 01:01:45,560
We're almost there. After these stairs...
就快到了  过了这几个台阶……

779
01:01:47,160 --> 01:01:48,880
We'll turn left, and then...
我们向左转，然后……

780
01:03:08,120 --> 01:03:11,160
Feza, forgive me. I know it was quite a walk.
费扎，原谅我，我知道那是很长的一段路

781
01:03:11,640 --> 01:03:15,360
But the elevator's always broken.
但是电梯总是坏

782
01:03:15,880 --> 01:03:17,560
Always broken. I don't know why.
总是坏  我不知道为什么

783
01:03:21,760 --> 01:03:23,040
Why won't it go in?
为什么不进去呢？

784
01:03:27,440 --> 01:03:28,920
They won't be home.
他们不会回来的

785
01:03:29,000 --> 01:03:31,600
The kids are both out. Don't ring the bell.
孩子们都出去了  别按门铃

786
01:03:35,800 --> 01:03:37,560
Don't ring the bell. There's nobody home.
别按门铃  没有人在家

787
01:03:38,960 --> 01:03:42,680
Feza, there's nobody home. Stop ringing the bell. That's enough.
费扎，没有人在家  别按门铃！

788
01:03:52,600 --> 01:03:53,760
Yes?
谁啊？

789
01:03:56,440 --> 01:03:57,720
Nezaket?
内扎凯特 ？

790
01:04:02,080 --> 01:04:03,360
It's Agah.
我是阿加

791
01:04:04,480 --> 01:04:07,160
Speak louder. I can't hear you.
大声说  我听不到你的声音

792
01:04:08,200 --> 01:04:09,320
Agah.
阿加

793
01:04:10,040 --> 01:04:11,400
Do you remember me?
你还记得我吗？

794
01:04:12,440 --> 01:04:14,760
I used to live here with my wife, Mebrure.
我曾经和我的妻子梅布鲁雷一起住在这里

795
01:04:14,840 --> 01:04:17,760
You were our landlord. Agah Beyoglu.
你是我们的房东  我是阿加·贝尤鲁

796
01:04:18,840 --> 01:04:20,240
Agah Beyoglu.
阿加·贝尤鲁

797
01:04:24,240 --> 01:04:25,640
Agah!
阿加！

798
01:04:26,200 --> 01:04:27,800
Come on in. Come in.
进来进来

799
01:04:28,560 --> 01:04:32,440
So, Agah... You wanted to see your old home?
那么，阿加  你是想看看你的老房子吗？

800
01:04:33,560 --> 01:04:35,400
I understand. It must be full of memories.
我能理解  这里一定充满回忆的

801
01:04:36,080 --> 01:04:39,200
We used to live upstairs, as you know.
如你所知，我们曾经住在楼上

802
01:04:39,280 --> 01:04:42,720
When Fikri died, I took a good look around.
菲克里去世后，我环顾四周

803
01:04:42,800 --> 01:04:47,720
Living on my own in a huge apartment wasn't going to work out.
我自己住在一个巨大的公寓里不行的

804
01:04:48,240 --> 01:04:49,560
So I came down here.
所以我搬下来了

805
01:04:50,520 --> 01:04:51,760
Tell you what.
告诉你吧

806
01:04:52,720 --> 01:04:55,840
Do you remember Iclal? My daughter?
你还记得伊克拉尔吗？我的女儿？

807
01:04:55,920 --> 01:04:58,080
She got married and moved to Ankara.
她结婚后搬到了安卡拉

808
01:04:58,160 --> 01:05:01,840
She never calls me anymore.
她再也没有打电话给我

809
01:05:01,920 --> 01:05:04,600
Why would someone neglect their own mother so much?
为什么会有人这么对待自己的母亲？

810
01:05:06,040 --> 01:05:08,080
Here's how it goes.
这是怎么回事

811
01:05:08,160 --> 01:05:13,360
I call her, she yawns and yawns on the other end.
我打电话给她，她不停的打哈欠

812
01:05:13,880 --> 01:05:16,520
When I ask what's wrong, she tells me she's getting sleepy.
当我问出什么问题时，她告诉我她很困

813
01:05:17,880 --> 01:05:19,480
It baffles me.
这让我感到困惑

814
01:05:20,680 --> 01:05:21,920
When she was a little girl...
当她还是一个小女孩时

815
01:05:22,560 --> 01:05:28,880
I'd swing her for hours, but she wouldn't get a wink of sleep.
我要把她摇摇晃晃几个小时，但她一点都不困

816
01:05:28,960 --> 01:05:35,680
Now, whenever I call to talk, she yawns and yawns.
现在，每当我打电话时，她都会哈欠

817
01:05:36,480 --> 01:05:39,400
When I ask what's wrong, she tells me she's getting sleepy.
当我问出什么问题时，她告诉我她很困

818
01:05:40,760 --> 01:05:43,640
So I stopped calling. What else was I supposed to do?
所以我不再打电话给她  我该怎么办？

819
01:05:44,680 --> 01:05:46,240
I had to accept it.
我不得不接受

820
01:05:47,360 --> 01:05:48,680
So?
那么？

821
01:05:48,760 --> 01:05:51,360
Where do you live now, Agah?
阿加，你现在住在哪里？

822
01:05:51,440 --> 01:05:53,440
Where do you live?
你住在哪里？

823
01:05:54,720 --> 01:05:57,880
- That's what I'm trying to remember. - What's that supposed to mean?
-这就是我试图记起来的  -什么意思？

824
01:05:58,560 --> 01:06:02,240
Don't you know where you live? Where your home is?
你不知道你住在哪里吗？你家在哪里？

825
01:06:07,680 --> 01:06:10,600
- What's Mebrure saying? - That's not Mebrure.
-梅布鲁雷在说什么？-她不是梅布鲁雷

826
01:06:11,840 --> 01:06:14,320
- Excuse me? - That's not Mebrure!
-什么？-她不是梅布鲁雷！

827
01:06:19,680 --> 01:06:23,240
I'm asking myself a different question. Why did I come here?
我在问自己一个不同的问题  我为什么要来这里？

828
01:06:24,640 --> 01:06:27,160
Might I have come here to kill you?
我可能会来这里杀死你吗？

829
01:06:28,000 --> 01:06:30,760
What are you saying? I can't hear you. Speak louder.
你在说什么  我听不到你  大点声

830
01:06:31,800 --> 01:06:35,200
Nezaket, have you ever been to Kambura?
内扎凯特，你去过坎布拉吗？

831
01:06:35,280 --> 01:06:37,600
- What? - Kambura!
-什么？-坎布拉！

832
01:06:38,480 --> 01:06:40,400
Have you ever been to Kambura?
你去过坎布拉吗？

833
01:06:41,160 --> 01:06:43,320
You're losing it.
你疯了

834
01:06:44,760 --> 01:06:45,760
Get off it!
别胡扯！

835
01:07:14,520 --> 01:07:17,040
DOG SLAYER
狗杀手

